":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"그렇군요……\n그러면… 실례합니다……\n……어라? 이 좋은 향기는…… 카레인가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"네! 사실 요즘 향신료부터 만드는 것에 빠져있거든요.\n저번에도 생일 선물로 Afterglow 멤버들한테\n향신료를 받았어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"향신료부터…… 카레를 만들다니……\n본격적이라…… 굉장하네요……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"의외로 간단한데, 여러 가지 신경 쓰는 게 재미있어요!\n같은 향신료라도 배분이나 불에 올리는 순서에 따라\n전혀 다른 맛이 나요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"2022birthdayMemorial-009-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect"